channel.description:
hey i dunno if this is the right section but please correct me if this isnt the right section ok i get this error for silab every time i load it up becuase i need the codes for silab for building my server
this is the error i get
sorry, an error has occured whilst loading silab client
try to fix these in order
try closing all open web-browser windows,and reload try clearing your web cache from tools>internet options try a different game world try rebooting you computer try selecting a different version of java from the game play menu
